{
  "stem": "15197.4",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "With the money, they came back to the old hiding place and the five survived.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And two, I met later in Israel.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So my task, after the Uprising, was to contact camps, to contact people in hiding, and what was only able to help them to survive.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Nobody has contact, during the Uprising, with the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You read sometimes in the Polish papers or books about contacts.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We, on the Polish side, the leadership, the few are were in contact-- one of our leaders was [NON-ENGLISH]-- he's dead already-- and he was in contact with the Polish underground.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We didn't have any direct contact, although some claim that in this and this part, some group of [NON-ENGLISH]-- of the liberal-- of the leftist, was helping them.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We didn't know at that time about this, at all.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They were alone.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "The ghetto was absolutely alone, forsaken.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And even today, when I think and I look back, history is being made-- by Poles or by others.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Our Jewish people were absolutely isolated and by themself.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I think that we have to remember this because history, sometimes, is being made by political groups.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And what is good for them and what the image they would like to be seen in history, they write it down.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But the reality was different.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "We were forsaken.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And I think that in the future, and even today, history has to inscribe the truthful fact how it was really.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "We were even forsaken by the allies-- by the outside world.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "By the so-called free world.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "We turned to them.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Later on, I was in the Polish Uprising.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And together with the Polish people as a Polish girl, I was witnessing how the planes came from England-- from London, from other places-- and they were dropping ammunition.",
      "word_count": 29
    }
  ],
